privileged = MAX_UNSIGNED_INT32_VALUE
nos = NumericOrderedSet(UNSIGNED_INT32, privileged)
length = 10
for i in range(length):
    assert len(nos) == i
    assert nos.add(i)
assert len(nos) == length
nos.add_privileged()
assert len(nos) == length + 1
nos.add(privileged)
assert len(nos) == length + 2
nos.clear()
assert len(nos) == 0
